attributes.title: New Year Edition
attributes.caption: Off for the Week!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff weren't in the office today, but they left us this nice little video.  Enjoy and check back soon for fresh new AHWU content!

attributes.title: Week #94
attributes.caption: 2012 and One
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back for a brand new year's worth of gaming goodness and news!  Okay, this week might start slowly, but I swear, 2012 will be awesome!

attributes.title: Week #95
attributes.caption: A dash of Joel
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff (with a hint of Joel) deliver you the greatest news known to man! You know you want it.  Oh, and buy a new Achievement Hunter shirt at http://roosterteeth.com/store and then follow us on Twitter at @roosterteeth, @achievementhunt, @geoffrvb, @jack_p, @ah_michael

attributes.title: Week #96
attributes.caption: WTF was that?
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver another delicious batch of gaming news and info in this week's AHWU.  Also, a giant creepy rooster thing.

attributes.title: Week #98
attributes.caption: Geoff is solo
attributes.description: Geoff is flying solo for this week's AHWU.  In it he talks about the newly released Darkness 2, some news about the Playstation Network and more!

attributes.title: Week #100
attributes.caption: A milestone!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff team up for the 100th episode of Achievement Hunter Weekly Update!  Watch them as they talk about all kinds of news and gaming.  But sure to buy tickets to RTX at http://rtxevent.com/ and watch for more!

attributes.title: Week #101
attributes.caption: After a milestone!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with AHWU #101!  Check out the news and information they provide and also check out RTX 2012 at http://www.rtxevent.com/

attributes.title: Week #102
attributes.caption: Week of Threes
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with another week of gaming news and information.  Watch and learn more about Assassin's Creed III, Mass Effect 3 and more!

attributes.title: Week #103
attributes.caption: With a new contest!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff (and sometimes Gavin) deliver you some of the freshest news and gaming coverage available.  Stay tuned all the way to the end to learn how you can win some cool prizes from http://insertcoinclothing.com/ and Achievement Hunter! Don't forget to like us on Facebook at http://facebook.com/AchievementHunter

attributes.title: Week #104
attributes.caption: Jack goes braindead
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with more gaming news.  Don't forget to send in your entry for the Soul Calibur 5 contest with prizes from InsertCoinClothing.com ! Hooray! Pay attention to when Jack forgets what he was saying in the news!

attributes.title: Week #105
attributes.caption: Gavin gets murdered
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with a weekly dose of goodies and fun funs.  Watch this week as Jack murders Gavin!

attributes.title: Week #106
attributes.caption: More Gavin Pain
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with more AHWU and gaming news.  Also watch as Jack slowly whittles away at Gavin's will to live!

attributes.title: Week #107
attributes.caption: Post PAX Pain
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with some game releases and news from the gaming world.  Watch as Jack slowly falls asleep and hurts Gavin again.

attributes.title: Week #108
attributes.caption: Lack of Gavin
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff talk about this week's upcoming titles including Trials Evolution and The Witcher 2!  Less Gavin punching this week.  Sorry.

attributes.title: Week #109
attributes.caption: Too Much Gavin
attributes.description: Jack and Gavin deliver you only the most important of news bites and blips in today's episode of AHWU.  Enjoy!

attributes.title: Week #110
attributes.caption: Gavin Dies Soon
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you another week's worth of news and gaming! Be amazed at how Gavin has yet to be murdered! Enjoy! Also, buy tickets for RTX! http://rtxevent.com/

attributes.title: Week #111
attributes.caption: Sell Outs!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff (and Gavin) bring you some new news in the world of gaming and other places.  Come for the information about The Elder Scrolls Online, stay for the Gavin punching.

attributes.title: Week #112
attributes.caption: Diablo Threeee
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are here to deliver you wonderful news in the gaming world! Did you know Diablo III is coming out  I did too! Woo!!

attributes.title: Week #113
attributes.caption: Gavino is Douchino
attributes.description: Jack and Gavin delivers you a heaping helping of delicious gaming news this week.  While Geoff is out, the kids will play!  Don't forget to buy your RTX tickets at http://www.rtxevent.com

attributes.title: Week #114
attributes.caption: Memorializing!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you a Memorial Day's worth of gaming news and information! Don't forget to catch Red vs. Blue premiering tonight at http://www.roosterteeth.com/ and buy your tickets for RTX at http://www.rtxevent.com/

attributes.title: Week #115
attributes.caption: A New Face at E3!
attributes.description: Jack and Achievement Hunter's newest face, Ali, talk about this week's releases and get psyched for a week of E3 in Los Angeles!

attributes.title: Week #116
attributes.caption: Back in Austin
attributes.description: Jack and Gavin take over AHWU this week to talk about Lollipops, Chainsaws, Stupid Sunglasses and more! Enjoy!

attributes.title: Week #117
attributes.caption: Halo-riffic!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you a Halo-riffic episode of AHWU. Watch and learn about everything coming up this week!

attributes.title: Week #118
attributes.caption: WET BEARD!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with more news and information from the world of vidjagames. Find out this week about Criterion, Spec Ops: The Line, Skyrim and more! Also, WET BEARD.

attributes.title: Week #119
attributes.caption: Pre-RTX
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff talk about all kinds of news and games in this week's AHWU. Find out more about RTX, Halo 4, Grifballs and more!

attributes.title: Week #120
attributes.caption: Post-RTX
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff survived RTX and bring you news from around the world of gaming and releases from around the world of other stuff.

attributes.title: Week #121
attributes.caption: Post-Comic-Con
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back and bringing you news from around the world of gaming! Watch and learn about this week's new releases on XBLA and DLC! Also, Halo 4 information and more!

attributes.title: Week #122
attributes.caption: 4th Anniversary AHWU!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you a week's worth of new games and information. Don't forget that this Friday is Achievement Hunter's 4th Anniversary! We'll be celebrating with a live stream on Friday afternoon.

attributes.title: Week #123
attributes.caption: Free stuff!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you another fantastic episode of AHWU. Watch this week's episode and learn how to get yourself a free beta key for the PC version of Awesomenauts! Free stuff rules! Also, watch Nature Town!

attributes.title: Week #124
attributes.caption: Including PS3 News!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff have another pile of delicious gaming news and information to share with you! Keep an eye on the Rooster Teeth store later this week for some cool new merch!

attributes.title: Week #125
attributes.caption: Watch your head
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with a bit of annoyance from the rest of the boys. Ray, watch your head.

attributes.title: Week #126
attributes.caption: Now with Steam!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are here to deliver you some hard hitting news in the world of gaming. Come for the STEAM news and stay for the cute girls announcing numbers.

attributes.title: Week #127
attributes.caption: From Toronto!
attributes.description: Jack brings Jordan and Barbara into the fold this week as AHWU travels to Toronto! Watch scenes from a sidewalk and an airport in this week's episode! Don't forget to check out Quick Bits! The newest show from Achievement Hunter!

attributes.title: Week #128
attributes.caption: PAX 2012 Edition!
attributes.description: Jack is out at PAX in Seattle so he had to find some backup to help him in this week's AHWU! Join him, Gus and Barbara (with special guest Eric from Mega64) as they talk about the week in games and other stuff! This episode of AHWU is brought to you by Game.Minder

attributes.title: Week #129
attributes.caption: Back Home
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with a whole slew of releases for the week. Keep your eye on the background to see if anything dumb happens. It does.

attributes.title: Week #130
attributes.caption: Special Secrets!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are here for another week of goodies! Don't forget to check out the special discount for the Rooster Teeth store! WATCH and learn!

attributes.title: Week #135
attributes.caption: Backpack!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you all the news that is fit to print in today's AHWU! Watch and learn about cool upcoming stuff and take a gander at the new Achievement Hunter backpacks that will be available soon in the Rooster Teeth store!

attributes.title: Week #138
attributes.caption: Nice Suit!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are here with more AHWU!

attributes.title: Week #139
attributes.caption: Weeee-You?
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are here with the first AHWU that is post-WiiU launch! How will it go This episode is brought to you by ONNIT and their flagship product Alpha Brain!

attributes.title: Week #140
attributes.caption: Turkey-Day
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring forth some news and game information for this post-Thanksgiving week!

attributes.title: Week #141
attributes.caption: Mouth Holes
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff and the rest of the crew bring you some awesome goodies from the world of gaming.

attributes.title: Week #142
attributes.caption: Christmas Time!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring all the news that is fit to print! This week's episode of AHWU is brought to you by Game.Minder!

attributes.title: Week #143
attributes.caption: Christmas Lights
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff and the boys are here with a ton of good news and information for you and your fellow gamer friends. Enjoy the hilarity!
